import React from 'react'

const Form = () => {
    return (
        <form className='flex  flex-col gap-5 sm:gap-8 md:gap-10'>
            <input className='p-1 bg-[#6B728E] text-slate-50 rounded-sm outline-none'
                placeholder='Username'
                type="text" />
            <input className='p-1 bg-[#6B728E] text-slate-50 rounded-sm outline-none'
                placeholder='Password'
                type="password" />

            <button className='bg-[#F2F7A1] py-1 font-bold  rounded-sm'>
                Login
            </button>
        </form>
    )
}

export default Form
